result:
.description
    .wrapper
        template(v-for="(card, i) in page.acf ? page.acf.editor : []")

            block-article(
                v-if="card.acf_fc_layout === 'Block 1'"
                :key="i"
                :title="card.field1",
                :text="card.field2"
            )

            block-text(
                v-if="card.acf_fc_layout === 'Block 7'"
                :key="i"
                :text="card.field1"
            )

            block-video(
                v-if="card.acf_fc_layout === 'Block 8'"
                :key="i"
                :link="card.field1"
            )

            block-blockquote(
                v-if="card.acf_fc_layout === 'Block 2'"
                :key="i"
                :text="card.field1"
            )

            block-img(
                v-if="card.acf_fc_layout === 'Block 3'"
                :key="i"
                :url="card.image.url"
            )

            block-table(
                v-if="card.acf_fc_layout === 'Block 6'"
                :key="i"
                :table="card.field1"
            )

            block-list(
                v-if="card.acf_fc_layout === 'Block 4'"
                :key="i"
                :list="card.field1"
            )

            block-opinion(
                v-if="card.acf_fc_layout === 'Block 9'"
                :key="i"
                :card="card"
            )

        social-block

    aside.description__sidebar(v-show="page.acf")
        card-winner
        card-app
        card-articles
    block-app#block-app(v-if="page.acf && page.acf.content.apps_1[0]" :app="getAppById(page.acf.content.apps_1[0].ID) || {}")
